paragraphs.text:
import org.apache.spark.sql.SQLContext

// Read CSV to RDD
val path = "/Users/kevincarey/code/scratch/spark-scratch/src/main/resources/baseballdatabank-master/core/Batting.csv"
val battingYears = new SQLContext(sc)
    .read
    .format("com.databricks.spark.csv")
    .option("header", "true")
    .option("inferSchema", "true")
    .load(path)
    .rdd

// Sum HR by playerID, save to table
battingYears
    .map(row => (row.getAs[String]("playerID"), Option(row.getAs[Int]("HR")).getOrElse(0)))
    .reduceByKey(_ + _)
    .toDF("playerId", "totalHomeRuns")
    .registerTempTable("players")

// Sum HR by year, save to table
battingYears
    .map(row => (row.getAs[Int]("yearID"), row.getAs[Int]("HR")))
    .reduceByKey(_ + _)
    .toDF("year", "totalHomeRuns")
    .registerTempTable("years")
    
// Sum HR by team, save to table
battingYears
    .map(row => ((row.getAs[String]("lgID"), row.getAs[Int]("yearID")), row.getAs[Int]("HR")))
    .reduceByKey(_ + _)
    .map(r => (r._1._1, r._1._2, r._2))
    .toDF("leagueId", "year", "totalHomeRuns")
    .registerTempTable("leagues")
